"{    \"translations\": [        {            \"english_version\": \"Lebanon's prime minister is happy about the new agreement. Hezbollah seems like it will follow the deal. We haven't heard anything from Israel yet.\",            \"english_title\": \"Lebanon Agreement\",            \"translated_version\": \"El primer ministro de L\u00edbano est\u00e1 feliz por el nuevo acuerdo. Parece que Hezbollah seguir\u00e1 el trato. No hemos escuchado nada de Israel todav\u00eda.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Acuerdo de L\u00edbano\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"A Ukrainian drone attack killed two people in Russia, according to Moscow. This happened after an Easter truce.\",            \"english_title\": \"Drone Attack in Russia\",            \"translated_version\": \"Un ataque de dron ucraniano mat\u00f3 a dos personas en Rusia, seg\u00fan Mosc\u00fa. Esto pas\u00f3 despu\u00e9s de una tregua de Pascua.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Ataque de Dron en Rusia\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"At least 16 people were hurt in a shooting at a high school on Tuesday. Then, nine more people were killed in another school shooting on Wednesday.\",            \"english_title\": \"School Shootings\",            \"translated_version\": \"Al menos 16 personas resultaron heridas en un tiroteo en una escuela secundaria el martes. Luego, nueve personas m\u00e1s murieron en otro tiroteo escolar el mi\u00e9rcoles.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Tiroteos en Escuelas\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Former Arsenal goalkeeper Alex Manninger died at 48 years old. His car was hit by a train.\",            \"english_title\": \"Alex Manninger Dies\",            \"translated_version\": \"El ex portero del Arsenal, Alex Manninger, muri\u00f3 a los 48 a\u00f1os. Su coche fue golpeado por un tren.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Muere Alex Manninger\"        },        {            \"english_version\": \"Investigators say Justin Fairfax shot his wife, Cerina, many times before he shot himself.\",            \"english_title\": \"Shooting Incident\",            \"translated_version\": \"Los investigadores dicen que Justin Fairfax dispar\u00f3 a su esposa, Cerina, muchas veces antes de dispararse a s\u00ed mismo.\",            \"translated_title\": \"Incidente de Tiroteo\"        }    ]}"